    <stitle>BODY CONTROLLER DIAGNOSTIC TROUBLE CODES - Displaying Diagnostic Trouble Codes</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec id="s0826301">
        <title>Displaying Diagnostic Trouble Codes</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>The ability to display diagnostic trouble codes (DTC) is an optional feature. Codes may be displayed
                on either the gauge cluster or an optional vehicle information display (VID).
                <emph type="bold">The vehicle must be equipped with the option to display codes in both cases.</emph>
                Codes will not be displayed on the gauge cluster if the vehicle is equipped with the VID.
            </para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
    </svcsubsec>
